bilingual.source: You must stand on the board and roll forward.
bilingual.target: 你必须站在板上向前滚动。

bilingual.source: The housekeeper leapt forward, her lips curled in a sneer.
bilingual.target: 管家向前跳去，嘴角露出讥笑。

bilingual.source: She breathed in, trembled, and stepped forward.
bilingual.target: 她吸了一口气，颤抖着，向前走了一步。

bilingual.source: "No!" shouted Zara, as the Silver Turtle rolled forward.
Then she leaned forward and put her hand on the yeti's arm.
bilingual.target: 然后她向前倾身，把手放在雪人的胳膊上。

bilingual.source: A ripple of applause starts at the back of the room and rolls forward like a wave.
bilingual.target: 一阵掌声从房间后面开始，像波浪一样向前滚动。

bilingual.source: He moved forward an inch at a time.
bilingual.target: 他一次向前移动一英寸。
她倾斜向前以便听得更清楚。

list.abstract: forward是服务器请求资源,服务器直接访问目标地址的URL，把那个URL的响应内容读取过来，然后把这些内容再发给浏览器。浏览器根本不知道服务器发送的内容从哪里来的，所以它的地址栏还是原来的地址。forward:转发页面和转发到的页面可以共享request里面的数据。

yingyinNormal.en: Remember, Daddy Pig, push the lever forward to go forward. Aye aye, Grandpa Pig.
yingyinNormal.zh: 记好了。把遥控杆向前推的话，船就会向前行驶。我明白了，猪爷爷。

yingyinNormal.en: With our friends moving forward in their relationships, I've decided that we should make progress in ours as well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 鉴于我们的朋友关系都正在向前发展，我决定我们的关系也该更进一步了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd like to move forward, but I need to know exactly what I was a part of, that... that I wasn't a part of someone's...
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想向前看，但是我需要知道我到底卷入了什么事情，确定我有没有卷入某人的...

yingyinNormal.en: That completely was a forward pass, which they threw intentionally incomplete to avoid loss of yardage or to conserve time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那完全就是个向前传球，也就是说他们故意传球不成功以免被罚码数或为了节省时间。

yingyinNormal.en: Forward. And back to go back. And Back, simple. And please look after my boat, I just had it painted.
yingyinNormal.zh: 向前推。然后往后拉就是倒退。往后拉，很简单。还有，请一定要保护好我的船，我才刚刚重新喷过漆。

yingyinNormal.en: About the only thing you can't do is ignore them. Because they change things. They push the human race forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只有一件事你不能做就是忽视他们，因为他们改变了一些东西，他们把人类推向前进

yingyinNormal.en: Please don't think us too forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请原谅我们的唐突。

yingyinNormal.en: So, what's your plan moving forward?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你接下来有什么计划？

yingyinNormal.en: That said. I look forward to seeing you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就这样， 期待见到你。

yingyinNormal.en: I will take your kindness, and pay it forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我感谢你的善良，我要报答你。

yingyinNormal.en: We progress forward until we encounter setbacks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们前进时会遇到挫折。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, it's so beautiful, so fashion forward, so Valentino.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美极了，时尚极了，很有华伦天奴的范儿。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's create some space over there. Move forward and out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请尽快空出一些位子。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm looking forward to the samples. We're all very proud.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我期待着样品出来，我们都很骄傲。

yingyinNormal.en: And look forward to reading your personal essays, 10,000 words.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我希望能够看到你们详细的陈述，10,000个字。

yingyinNormal.en: Look forward. No emotion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 目光直视前方，不要带情绪。

yingyinNormal.en: We are not here to negotiate! You want forward-thinking, Bob? Then think forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不是来谈判的，你要放眼未来吗？鲍勃，快放眼看啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Hank you weren't being forward. That's kind of what I meant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 汉克，你没有太直接，这也是我的意思。

yingyinNormal.en: Though I can't say you'll be much a marksman moving forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过只怕不能当行动风如的神枪手了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll be back to check on Jane in a week. I look forward to it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一周后我再来给简检查。我很期待。

examination_example.sentence: The court's ruling is a step <highlight>forward</highlight> in the struggle against both corruption and official favoritism.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最高法院的裁决是在与腐败、“公务偏袒”这两者的斗争中所取得的一个进步。

examination_example.sentence: At least we are now finally moving <highlight>forward</highlight> at a faster pace.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 至少我们现在终于以更快的速度前进。

examination_example.sentence: When our time of mourning is over, we press <highlight>forward</highlight>, stronger with a greater understanding and respect for life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我们哀悼的时间结束时，我们继续生活下去，更加坚强并且更加理解和尊重生命。

sense_info_list.en: relating to or concerned with the future

examination_example.sentence: It surely seems plausible that happy people would be more <highlight>forward</highlight>-thinking and creative and lean towards R&D more than the average.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 快乐的人会比普通人更有前瞻性和创造性，更倾向于R&D，这似乎是合理的。

examination_example.sentence: You might even be tempted to assume that humanity has little future to look <highlight>forward</highlight> to.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 您也许甚而被诱惑假设，人类有一点未来盼望。

sense_info_list.en: directed or facing toward the front or the direction that one is facing or traveling

examination_example.sentence: Meanwhile, the asocial robot simply moved <highlight>forwards</highlight> and backwards and side to side.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，反社交机器人只是简单地前后左右移动。
